examples.text: Mr. <w>McCracken</w> has been teaching history at the local high school for over twenty years.
The <w>McCracken</w> family reunion is held every summer in the central park.

senses.sense_definition: A city in Rush County, Kansas, United States.

examples.text: They stopped in <w>McCracken</w> to refuel during their long road trip across Kansas.
The population of <w>McCracken</w> is quite small compared to the state capital.
